## ğŸ“– Story Types & Estimation

### Labels
- **Feature** â€“ new behavior or enhancement
- **Bug** â€“ defect or regression
- **Chore** â€“ maintenance or infra work

### Estimation Scale (Fibonacci)
- `0`: trivial fixes
- `1`: straightforward task
- `2`: medium complexity
- `3+`: complex or multi-step (break into smaller stories if possible)

### Prompt
> â€œGiven this user story, classify it and estimate complexity using Fibonacci scale. Justify the estimate.â€

